## About R'tichoke

R'tichoke is a dedicated repository of R programming content, tutorials, and resources. 

Feel free to reach out on [LinkedIn!](https://linkedin.com/in/riddhimanr) 

## How This Site Works

All content on this site is created using [Quarto](https://quarto.org/), a next-generation version of R Markdown. This allows us to:

1. Write content in `.qmd` files (Quarto Markdown)
2. Include executable R code chunks
3. Generate beautiful, interactive web pages
4. Create a consistent, organized structure

## R Resources

Here are some additional resources for learning R:

- [R Project for Statistical Computing](https://www.r-project.org/)
- [RStudio](https://posit.co/products/open-source/rstudio/)
- [Tidyverse](https://www.tidyverse.org/)
- [R for Data Science](https://r4ds.had.co.nz/)
- [R-bloggers](https://www.r-bloggers.com/)
